{"metadata":{"symbolKind":"method","modules":[{"name":"GLibObject"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Method","title":"addToggleRef(notify:data:)","role":"symbol","extendedModule":"GLibObject","externalID":"s:10GLibObject0B8ProtocolPAAE12addToggleRef6notify4datayySvSg_SpySo8_GObjectVGSgs5Int32VtXCSg_AGtF::SYNTHESIZED::s:10GLibObject10BindingRefV","fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"addToggleRef","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"notify"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"GToggleNotify","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:gobject.h@T@GToggleNotify"},{"text":"?, ","kind":"text"},{"text":"data","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:gtypes.h@T@gpointer","text":"gpointer"},{"text":"?)","kind":"text"}]},"sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject","doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/BindingRef","doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/BindingRef\/ObjectProtocol-Implementations"]]},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/BindingRef\/addToggleRef(notify:data:)","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"abstract":[{"text":"Increases the reference count of the object by one and sets a","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"callback to be called when all other references to the object are","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"dropped, or when this is already the last reference to the object"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and another reference is established."}],"kind":"symbol","variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/glibobject\/bindingref\/addtoggleref(notify:data:)"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"addToggleRef"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"text":"notify","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"GToggleNotify","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:gobject.h@T@GToggleNotify"},{"text":"?, ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"data"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"gpointer","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:gtypes.h@T@gpointer"},{"kind":"text","text":"? = nil)"}],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"content":[{"text":"Discussion","level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This functionality is intended for binding "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"object"},{"text":" to a proxy","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"object managed by another memory manager. This is done with two"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"paired references: the strong reference added by"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_add_toggle_ref()"},{"text":" and a reverse reference to the proxy","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"object which is either a strong reference or weak reference.","type":"text"}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The setup is that when there are no other references to "},{"code":"object","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":","},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"only a weak reference is held in the reverse direction from ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"object"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to the proxy object, but when there are other references held to"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"object"},{"type":"text","text":", a strong reference is held. The "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"notify"},{"type":"text","text":" callback is called"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"when the reference from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"object"},{"type":"text","text":" to the proxy object should be"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"“toggled” from strong to weak ("},{"code":"is_last_ref","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" true) or weak to strong"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"(","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"is_last_ref"},{"text":" false).","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Since a (normal) reference must be held to the object before","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"calling "},{"code":"g_object_add_toggle_ref()","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", the initial state of the reverse","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"link is always strong."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Multiple toggle references may be added to the same gobject,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"however if there are multiple toggle references to an object, none"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"of them will ever be notified until all but one are removed.  For"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"this reason, you should only ever use a toggle reference if there","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"is important state in the proxy object."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Note that if you unref the object on another thread, then ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"notify"},{"type":"text","text":" might"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"still be invoked after "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_remove_toggle_ref()"},{"type":"text","text":", and the object argument"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"might be a dangling pointer. If the object is destroyed on other threads,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"you must take care of that yourself."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A "},{"code":"g_object_add_toggle_ref()","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" must be released with "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_remove_toggle_ref()"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]}],"kind":"content"}],"references":{"doc://GLibObject/documentation/GLibObject/BindingRef":{"kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"BindingRef","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"BindingRef","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GObject"},{"text":" instance (or source) and another property on another ","type":"text"},{"code":"GObject","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"instance (or target).","type":"text"}],"role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/glibobject\/bindingref","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/BindingRef","type":"topic","title":"BindingRef"},"doc://GLibObject/documentation/GLibObject/BindingRef/addToggleRef(notify:data:)":{"role":"symbol","title":"addToggleRef(notify:data:)","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"addToggleRef"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"notify","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"text":"GToggleNotify","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:gobject.h@T@GToggleNotify"},{"kind":"text","text":"?, "},{"text":"data","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"gpointer","preciseIdentifier":"c:gtypes.h@T@gpointer"},{"text":"?)","kind":"text"}],"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/glibobject\/bindingref\/addtoggleref(notify:data:)","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Increases the reference count of the object by one and sets a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"callback to be called when all other references to the object are"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"dropped, or when this is already the last reference to the object","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and another reference is established."}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/BindingRef\/addToggleRef(notify:data:)"},"doc://GLibObject/documentation/GLibObject/BindingRef/ObjectProtocol-Implementations":{"type":"topic","role":"collectionGroup","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/BindingRef\/ObjectProtocol-Implementations","title":"ObjectProtocol Implementations","abstract":[],"kind":"article","url":"\/documentation\/glibobject\/bindingref\/objectprotocol-implementations"},"doc://GLibObject/documentation/GLibObject":{"role":"collection","kind":"symbol","abstract":[],"identifier":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject","url":"\/documentation\/glibobject","title":"GLibObject","type":"topic"}}}